     Bb/G can safely be written as Gmin7, but in this recording in the place you are talking about, the bass is not G, it's C. seems like that chord is like C7, .... with F# in there .... so like C9#11? but it also sounds like the keyboard and guitarist are not entirely on the same page here. the keyboardist sounds like he thinks the chord is C7. and the guitarist sounds like he would rather not worry about it
